out_to_x no
background no
cpu_avg_samples 2
net_avg_samples 2
no_buffers yes
out_to_console yes
out_to_stderr no
extra_newline no
update_interval 1.0
uppercase no
use_spacer left

## Colors are in dzen2 format.
TEXT
^fg(grey)${time %a %d %b %R} \
       \
^fg(grey)CPU: ^fg(DeepSkyBlue)$cpu% \
^fg(grey)RAM: ^fg(DeepSkyBlue)$memperc% \
^fg(grey)RX: ^fg(DeepSkyBlue)${downspeedf eth0} \
^fg(grey)TX: ^fg(DeepSkyBlue)${upspeedf eth0} \
^fg(grey)sda: ^fg(DeepSkyBlue)${diskio sda}

